page.title: 09Jillian's Travels
page.content: My name is Jillian Summerfield.I am 11 years old.I have one brother called Gary.We live in Glenrothes though we have not lived there all our lives.The earliest thing I remember is going on a plane in Prestwick Airport in Glasgow to Brunei.I was 5 then.In Brunei we went to infant school which was primary 1 to 4.There was junior school which was primary 5 to 7.You went to Singapore for High School.I did ballet and swam as well.Altogether we lived in Brunei for 18 months with spells of leave in Britain occasionally.We came back to Dundee and I went back to my old school there and met my friends again.My Dad got a new job so we had to move to Glenrothes.I joined Pitteuchar West Primary which is the school I attend at the moment.
